a rescue mission.

40
00:23:44.361 --> 00:23:47.819
Me? I knew you'd be okay.

41
00:23:49.132 --> 00:23:51.396
That's the thing
about cockroaches.

42
00:23:51.468 --> 00:23:54.904
No matter how many times
you flush them
down the toilet...

43
00:23:54.971 --> 00:23:57.462
they always crawl
back up the bowl.

44
00:23:58.408 --> 00:24:01.241
Hey. buddy?
I'm out of the bowl.

45
00:24:02.012 --> 00:24:04.674
I'm dryin' off my wings
and trekkin' across the lid.

46
00:24:12.622 --> 00:24:13.850
Driscoll!

47
00:24:15.325 --> 00:24:18.988
Don't be a fool!
Give it up. It's useless!

48
00:24:20.263 --> 00:24:21.628
She's dead.

49
00:24:24.434 --> 00:24:25.992
She's not dead.

50
00:24:29.906 --> 00:24:32.136
Jack's gonna bring her back...

51
00:24:33.109 --> 00:24:35.703
and the ape will be
hard on his heels.

52
00:24:36.413 --> 00:24:38.938
We can still
come out of this thing okay.

53
00:24:41.551 --> 00:24:43.109
More than okay.

54
00:24:44.354 --> 00:24:45.912
Think about it.

55
00:24:45.989 --> 00:24:48.822
