Look after yourself!

62
00:25:22.125 --> 00:25:23.752
Keep the gate open. will you?

63
00:25:24.127 --> 00:25:25.526
Sure thing. buddy.

64
00:25:26.563 --> 00:25:27.894
Good luck!

65
00:25:41.177 --> 00:25:42.542
